!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\n**Italiano**\n\nGestione tipi documento fiscale TD16, TD17, TD18, TD19 in generazione fattura elettronica.\n\nIl modulo permette di impostare, nell'XML, il corretto fornitore in caso di reverse charge.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Configuration\n\n**Italiano**\n\nVedi `l10n_it_reverse_charge` per la configurazione dei tipi di reverse charge.\n\nPer le autofatture da comunicare a SDI va impostato\n\n**Tipo partner** = **Altro**\n\ne\n\n**Partner autofattura** = **My company**\n\nSul tipo di reverse charge impostare anche il relativo **Tipo documento fiscale**\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/l10n-italy/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us smashing it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/l10n-italy/issues/new?body=module:%20l10n_it_fatturapa_out_rc%0Aversion:%2012.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- TAKOBI\n\n### Contributors\n\n- [TAKOBI](https://takobi.online):\n\n  - Lorenzo Battistini\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nCurrent [maintainer](https://odoo-community.org/page/maintainer-role):\n\n{{ maintainer-eLBati }}\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/l10n-italy](https://github.com/OCA/l10n-italy/tree/12.0/l10n_it_fatturapa_out_rc) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_it_fatturapa_out_rc.wizard", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_it_fatturapa_out_rc.wizard.wizard_export_e_invoice", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.l10n_it_fatturapa_out_rc.wizard..wizard_export_e_invoice", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_it_fatturapa_out_rc.models", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_it_fatturapa_out_rc.models.account_invoice", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.l10n_it_fatturapa_out_rc.models..account_invoice", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_it_fatturapa_out_rc.models.rc_type", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.l10n_it_fatturapa_out_rc.models..rc_type", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_it_fatturapa_out_rc.models.rc_type", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_it_fatturapa_out_rc.models.rc_type.AccountRCType", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_it_fatturapa_out_rc.models.rc_type.AccountRCType._inherit", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_it_fatturapa_out_rc.models.rc_type.AccountRCType.fiscal_document_type_id", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_it_fatturapa_out_rc.models.account_invoice", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_it_fatturapa_out_rc.models.account_invoice.Invoice", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [{"name": "odoo.